parameters.name: NatGatewayId
parameters.description: The ID of the Network Address Translation (NAT) gateway.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The page number. Pages start from page **1**.

Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries per page. The maximum value is **100**.

Default value: **10**.

parameters.name: SnatEntryId
parameters.description: The ID of the SNAT entry.

parameters.name: SnatEntryName
parameters.description: The name of the SNAT entry.

parameters.name: SnatIp
parameters.description: The elastic IP address (EIP) specified in the SNAT entry.

parameters.name: SourceCIDR
parameters.description: The source CIDR block specified in the SNAT entry.
